overview.eaover:
Data files include:

Braun-Blanquet cover/abundance data, FIAN_BB_Data s05_f09.xls;
seagrass metric data, FIAN_Blade_Data s05_f07.xls;
invertebrate data, FIAN_Crustacean_Data s05_f09.xls;
fish data, FIAN_Fish_Data s05_f09.xls;
animal size data, FIAN_Size_Data s05_s09.xls;
seagrass harvest data, FIAN_Standing_Crop_Data s05_s07.xls; and
field data, FIAN_Station_Data s05_f09.xls.
